<h1> Evening Pages </h1>
<form action='/pm_entries/<%=@pm_entry.id%>' method="POST">
	<input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PATCH">
	<h4>Two things today that went really well or exceeded my expectations were:
  	<h4>1. <input type="text" name="excellent1" value="<%=@pm_entry.excellent1%>" style="width: 600px;" </h4><br>
	<h4>2. <input type="text" name="excellent2" value="<%=@pm_entry.excellent2%>" style="width: 600px;" </h4><br>
	<h4>Three lessons I learned today, or ways I could have made the day better:</h4>
	<h4>1. <input type="text" name="lessons1" value="<%=@pm_entry.lessons1%>" style="width: 600px;" </h4><br>
	<h4>2. <input type="text" name="lessons2" value="<%=@pm_entry.lessons2%>" style="width: 600px;" </h4><br>
	<h4>3. <input type="text" name="lessons3" value="<%=@pm_entry.lessons3%>" style="width: 600px;" </h4><br>
	<h4>Five things I am grateful for right now are:</h4>
	<h4>1. <input type="text" name="gratitude1" value="<%=@pm_entry.gratitude1%>" style="width: 600px;"</h4><br>
	<h4>2. <input type="text" name="gratitude2" value="<%=@pm_entry.gratitude2%>" style="width: 600px;"</h4><br>
	<h4>3. <input type="text" name="gratitude3" value="<%=@pm_entry.gratitude3%>" style="width: 600px;"</h4><br>
	<h4>4. <input type="text" name="gratitude4" value="<%=@pm_entry.gratitude4%>" style="width: 600px;"</h4><br>
	<h4>5. <input type="text" name="gratitude5" value="<%=@pm_entry.gratitude5%>" style="width: 600px;"</h4><br>
	<h4>Additional thoughts/words:</h4>
	<h4><textarea name="thoughts" cols="40" rows="5"><%=@pm_entry.thoughts%> </textarea></h4>
	<input type="submit" value="Save Changes">
</form>
<form action="/main_menu">
	<input type="submit"class="button" value="Back to Main Menu">
</form>
<form action="/index">
	<input type="submit"class="button" value="Return to Index">
</form>
